name: The Mass Chicken Slaughter
description: In other parts of the world, there was a mass slaughter of chickens, because it was identified that they were infected with the bird flu virus. Almost all of the farms in the area were annihilated. Will this have an impact to where King Indukayam lives? And, does the king know about this? And is this H51N virus made by humans and the mutants? This case needs to be investigated.
